    <main class="w-100">
        <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center p-4 text-white min-vh-100">
            <h1 class="text-center mb-5" style="font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;">Security Tips</h1>
            <p>Keep your accounts safe by following these best practices for password security and online safety.</p>
            <div class="container-fluid text-dark rounded w-100">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row g-4 mt-5">
                        <!-- Card 1 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card card-tips h-100 text-center">
                                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                    <i class="bi bi-lock-fill mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Use Strong Passwords</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Create passwords that are at least 12 characters long and
                                        include a mix of letters, numbers, and symbols.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
                                   
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Card 2 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card card-tips h-100 text-center">
                                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                    <i class="bi bi-shield-check mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Enable Two-Factor Authentication</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Add an extra layer of security by enabling two-factor
                                        authentication on your accounts.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
                                   
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Card 3 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card card-tips h-100 text-center">
                                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                    <i class="bi bi-key mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Use Unique Passwords for Different Accounts</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Avoid using the same password across multiple sites. This
                                        reduces the risk if one account is compromised.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
                                    
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Card 4 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card card-tips h-100 text-center">
                                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                    <i class="bi bi-calendar-check mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Update Your Passwords Regularly</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Change your passwords periodically to enhance security.
                                        Consider setting reminders for password updates.</p>
                                        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
                                    
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Card 5 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card card-tips h-100 text-center">
                                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                    <i class="bi bi-gear mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Review Account Permissions</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Regularly review and adjust permissions for your online
                                        accounts to ensure they have access only to what is necessary.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Learn More</a>
                                   
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Card 6 -->
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <div class="card card-tips h-100 text-center">
                                <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                                    <i class="bi bi-cloud-arrow-up mb-3" style="font-size: 2rem;"></i>
                                    <h5 class="card-title">Backup Important Data</h5>
                                    <p class="card-text">Regularly backup important data to a secure location to prevent
                                        loss in case of an incident.</p>
                                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">Learn More</a>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="container mt-5">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-5 text-white mt-5">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
                        <div class="text-white text-center mb-5">
                            <p>We understand that managing security and passwords can raise many questions. 
                                Below, we've addressed some of the most common queries to help you stay informed and secure.
                                If you have any additional questions or need further assistance, 
                                please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team or consult our resources.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                                    <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                                        <i class="bi bi-shield-lock-fill me-2"></i> What is Two-Factor Authentication?
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne"
                                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) adds an extra layer of security by requiring not
                                        only a password but also a second factor, such as a code sent to your phone.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                                        <i class="bi bi-key-fill me-2"></i> How can I create a strong password?
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo"
                                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        A strong password should be at least 12 characters long and include a mix of uppercase and lowercase letters, 
                                        numbers, and special characters. Avoid using easily guessable information such as your name or birthdate.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                                        <i class="bi bi-clock-history me-2"></i> How Often Should I Change My Password?
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree"
                                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        It is recommended to change your password every 3 to 6 months or sooner if you
                                        suspect your account has been compromised.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                                        <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill me-2"></i> What should I do if I think my password has been compromised?
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour"
                                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        If you suspect your password has been compromised, immediately change the password for the affected account.
                                        Also, review and update passwords for other accounts where you may be using the same password. 
                                        If possible, enable two-factor authentication on all your accounts.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                                        <i class="bi bi-box-fill me-2"></i> What are the benefits of using a password manager?
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive"
                                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        A password manager helps you securely store and manage all your passwords in one place.
                                        It also offers features like generating strong passwords, 
                                        automatically filling in login details, and monitoring for data breaches.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="accordion-item">
                                <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingSix">
                                    <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                                        data-bs-target="#collapseSix" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseSix">
                                        <i class="bi bi-lock-fill me-2"></i> What are the best ways to protect my personal data online?
                                    </button>
                                </h2>
                                <div id="collapseSix" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingSix"
                                    data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                    <div class="accordion-body">
                                        Use strong and unique passwords, enable two-factor authentication, regularly review privacy settings on social media,
                                        and be cautious when sharing personal information online.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                           
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</div>
</div>

